---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Martial Arts Classes Perth - Ju Jutsu, Aikido, Tai Chi | Jan de Jong Martial Arts" description="Explore our martial arts classes in Perth. Ju Jutsu, Aikido, Tai Chi, Self Defence, Weapons Training. Expert instruction since 1952. Classes for all ages and abilities.">
  <section class="relative h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/classes-hero.jpg');">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading uppercase mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">Classes</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-width">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center mb-12">WE TRAIN YOU</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/jujutsu.jpg" alt="Ju Jutsu" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Ju Jutsu</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Ju Jutsu is the ancient Japanese art of self defence used by the Samurai in feudal Japan. Ju Jutsu is a comprehensive system of self defence which can be described
            </p>
            <Button href="/ju-jutsu">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/aikido.jpg" alt="Aikido" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Aikido</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Aikido ('way of harmony') is an unarmed method of self defence founded in Japan in 1942 by Morihei Ueshiba and is based on the principle of harmony
            </p>
            <Button href="/aikido-perth">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/specialised_training.jpg" alt="Specialised Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Specialised Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Ideal for specialised professions such as police, security officers, mine site controllers, journalists, nurses or any other groups or individuals requiring
            </p>
            <Button href="/specialised-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/stick_traing.jpg" alt="Stick Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Stick Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              There are stories of armed samurai being defeated by peasants with a jo (150cm stick). These are weapons not to be under-estimated.
            </p>
            <Button href="/stick-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/sword_training.jpg" alt="Sword Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Sword Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness offer specific Iai and Kenjutsu Training (Sword). Classes will address basic sword handling and kata taken
            </p>
            <Button href="/sword-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/self_defence.jpg" alt="Self Defence" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Self Defence</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              "Self defence is a basic life skill which most women will find useful at least once in their life time." You will be taught a number of self defence techniques
            </p>
            <Button href="/self-defence">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/self_protection.jpg" alt="Self Protection" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Self Protection</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              "Self defence is a basic life skill, which unfortunately many people will need at sometime in their life." Inherent in the Self Protection Course for Men & Women
            </p>
            <Button href="/self-protection">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/personal_training.jpg" alt="Personal Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Personal Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Personal Training Lessons are a way of improving on particular areas to meet your needs. We can address job or martial arts specific needs.
            </p>
            <Button href="/personal-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/corporate_training.jpg" alt="Corporate Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Corporate Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our Corporate Training offers in house or at our premises training ranging from "one off" delivered safety talks to "hands on" full participation short
            </p>
            <Button href="/corporate-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/security_training.jpg" alt="Security Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Security Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              The senior instructor of Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness, Paul Connolly, has worked with the Security Industry since 1982 and is able to offer solutions
            </p>
            <Button href="/security-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/tai_chi.jpg" alt="Tai Chi" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Tai Chi</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Ancient Chinese martial art combining gentle flowing movements, deep breathing, and meditation for health and wellbeing.
            </p>
            <Button href="/tai-chi">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded shadow-card overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/weapons_training.jpg" alt="Weapons Training" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-3">Weapons Training</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Traditional Japanese weapons training including sword, stick, and other classical martial arts weapons for advanced students.
            </p>
            <Button href="/sword-training">Read More</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center mb-8">MEET YOUR INSTRUCTORS</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          Instructors at Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness are acclaimed for their high level of technical knowledge and teaching ability. Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness commenced teaching at colleges and schools in Perth over 40 years ago. All classes are conducted in a positive, friendly atmosphere of cooperation, not competition. All students are encouraged to support and help each other, ensuring an enjoyable and fruitful learning experience. Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness has taught self defence in Perth since 1952. All instructors are students of, and have graded in, Jan de Jong Martial Arts, and have many years of experience up to more than 40 years. Our aim is to equip students to go about their daily life with quiet confidence knowing that they have efficient skills to protect themselves should the need arise.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <img src="/images/maggie-de-jong-scaled.jpg" alt="Maggie de Jong" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-2">MAGGIE DE JONG</h3>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Owner / Instructor</h4>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <img src="/images/paul-connoly-scaled.jpg" alt="Paul Connolly" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-2">PAUL CONNOLLY</h3>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Instructor</h4>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <img src="/images/daryl-cook-scaled.jpg" alt="Daryl Cook" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-2">DARYL COOK</h3>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Instructor</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center bg-accent p-8 rounded">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">BOOK A FREE TRIAL</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Memberships are purchased online or in the dojo as either pre-paid or subscription options. 
          There are separate memberships for adults, students, and children.
        </p>
        <Button href="/free-trial">Free Trial</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>